  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Daily 164：别霸凌自己]]></title>
    <link href="https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2026/05/20/daily-164/"/>
    <updated>2026-05-20T07:47:09+08:00</updated>
    <id>https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2026/05/20/daily-164</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>马斯克说的：<br/>
我不介意被人讨厌。<br/>
渴望被人喜欢才是弱点。<br/>
太在意别人的评价是对自己的霸凌。<br/>
Don&rsquo;t bully yourself.<br/>
As Elon Musk put it:<br/>
I don&rsquo;t mind being disliked.<br/>
The desire to be liked is a weakness.<br/>
Caring too much about others' judgments is bullying yourself.</p>
]]></content>
